l things are possible  </div><div class="t mac7 x70 he y150 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to him that believeth.&apos; . . . With the per-</div><div class="t m76a x70 he yd9 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">servering faith of Jacob, with the unyielding </div><div class="t m3e5 x70 he y662 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">persistence of Elijah, we may present our </div><div class="t m45b x70 he y125 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">petitions to the Father, claiming all that He </div><div class="t m5b5 x70 he y6 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">has promised. The honor of His throne is </div><div class="t m808 x70 he yb5 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">staked for the fulfillment of His word.&quot;—</div><div class="t mf9 x70 h21 y48c ff6 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Prophets and Kings, </div><div class="t m1bb7 xbe he y48c ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">pages 157, 158. </div><div class="t m41c x8 he yb8 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">10. </div><div class="t m445 x3d he yb8 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What fact in our Lord&apos;s great </div><div class="t m1132 x70 he y31b ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">prophecy, not mentioned by other </div><div class="t ma8a x70 he yd ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Gospel writers, is clearly • stated by </div><div class="t m100e x70 he ya58 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">this author? Mark 13:24. </div><div class="t m48d x4b he y10 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">NorE.—&quot;Twenty-five years later [than </div><div class="t m3bb x70 he y55e ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the tribulation] appeared the next sign </div><div class="t m9d0 x70 he ye5 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">mentioned in the prophecy,—the darkening </div><div class="t macf x70 he y28d ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of the sun and moon.&quot;—The </div><div class="t m7fa xe8 h21 y368 ff6 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Great Contro-</div><div class="t mf9 x70 h21 y15e ff6 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">versy, </div><div class="t mb1e x23 he y390 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">page 306. These signs occurred in a </div><div class="t ma0c x21 he yc2 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">short period of time referred to